{"tid":1913643,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警狗打壓港台，其實係進一步打壓言論自由","createTime":"2020-03-07T03:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T03:52:50.000Z","uid":278088,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7801e0ae3b994a5238a9a77cd693cba5c16e31d1","tid":1913643,"uid":278088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:26:28.000Z","msg":"吳志森講警狗對港台打壓比外表睇得更嚴重！<br />\n佢最後有講到要張呢隻事搬上<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">國際</span></strong></span>先有用！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為係講緊<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>一堆警狗竟然干預言論自由</strong></span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有無人幫到手？</strong></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=tmV7uU2KKWk&amp;feature=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtmV7uU2KKWk%26feature%3Dshare&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnOr6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=849dc14a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=tmV7uU2KKWk&amp;feature=share</a>"},{"pid":"8f1d0e8908c5b7ca70a916d1909a23898acbe7ad","tid":1913643,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:27:09.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n脫離支那是是香港唯一出路，但絕不能直接獨立，必須先經英美託管一段時間再經公投獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e669375f697f5455b3087008d5b5135de85d9a03","tid":1913643,"uid":54653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s6wewqr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs6wewqr.jpg&h=08459d2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nxN5C5r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnxN5C5r.jpg&h=8d3eedfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f9fd63952678c4390f7398d80f2254afbaa77ac","tid":1913643,"uid":8091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:30:54.000Z","msg":"大家正視問題"},{"pid":"e46824f7765d8d2814fedd2424040cc6debbb84f","tid":1913643,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:52:50.000Z","msg":"TWITTER手足現身喇要"}]}